## Chunk 4b — Search bar UI

**Goal:** Frameless, always-on-top, dark-mode `QWidget` that captures
user input and emits a debounced `queryChanged(QString)` signal.

### In scope
- `SearchOverlay` extends `QWidget` with
  `Qt::FramelessWindowHint | Qt::WindowStaysOnTopHint | Qt::Tool`.
- Single `QLineEdit` styled via QSS for dark mode.
- 30 ms debounce timer on `textChanged`.
- `Esc` triggers `closeRequested()` (handled in Chunk 5).
- Position: centred horizontally on the active screen, 20% from top.

### Definition of done
- 5 keystrokes within 30 ms emit only one `queryChanged` signal.
- Visual snapshot test of the bar across light/dark themes.

### Effort
~2 dev-days.

